                </a>
                <p class="header-desc">Complete managed hosting. Only worry about blogging, not server maintenance</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="/how-to-install-ghost-on-digital-ocean-vps">
                    <img class="img-circle img-responsive" src="assets/images/DO.png">
